COVID-19 mortality and long-term care: a UK comparison

Code to accompany the report published by the International Long-Term Care Policy Network here

Authors: David Bell, Adelina Comas-Heras, David Henderson, Sin Jones, Elizabeth Lemmon, Mirko Moro, Siobhn Murphy, Dermot OReilly, Pietro Patrignani.

Information

The code used to create plots and summary figures for the above report are available here from the links at the top of the page.

  • File 1 shows the wrangling of data from each nations care inspectorate body to enable further analysis in file 2
  • File 2 details code to produce Figures 1-3 and some summary statistics for table 1 in the report
  • File 3 shows code and summary statistics for the Excess deaths section of the report (Figures 5 and 6)

Raw code and data can be found on the project GitHub page

Plots on these pages (and saved on the project GitHub page) contain titles and captions unlike those used in the report which contains this infomation in-text.
